name: Ancient Aftershock
description:
Unleash a wave of anima, dealing 1,158 Nature damage to up to 5 enemies and knocking them down for 1.5 sec.

The ground will continue to expel anima, dealing 739 Nature damage to up to 5 enemies and generating 16 Rage per enemy over 12 sec. Every 3 sec, targets are briefly knocked down.
